SYNOPSIS

    In dist.ini:

        [InstallGuide]

DESCRIPTION

    This plugin adds a very simple INSTALL file to the distribution,
    telling the user how to install this distribution.

    You should use this plugin in your Dist::Zilla configuration after
    [MakeMaker] or [ModuleBuild] so that it can determine what kind of
    distribution you are building and which installation instructions are
    appropriate.

METHODS

 gather_files

    Creates the INSTALL file.

 munge_files

    Inserts the appropriate installation instructions into INSTALL.

